    • Method Detail

      • getVaadinRelativePathForResource

        public static java.lang.String getVaadinRelativePathForResource(java.lang.String relativeResourcePath)

        Returns a real-time relative path of the desired resource that can be included statically in HTML. The resource is required to be in vaadin's static resource folder, e.g. "WebContent/VAADIN/themes/{theme-name}/".

        Parameters:
        relativeResourcePath - theme-relative path to a file
